node.text:
I’m so glad I chose to partner with @NYXCosmetics on their #proudalliesforall campaign! My girlfriend @meloo00.9 is my ally and I’m so happy to have her on this journey with me. This experience with NYX has taught me the value of having that special someone in your corner to make you feel confident and beautiful. As a member of the LGBTQ community, I want to thank you all for being so supportive and supporting our campaign. Happy Pride Month ❤️🧡💛💚💙💜
#nyxcosmetics #nyxcosmeticspartner #proudalliesforall

node.text: I’m so proud to announce my official partnership with @nyxcosmetics for their #proudalliesforall campaign! We have been working on this for the past few months and I’m so excited to share my story with the rest of the world as a member of the LGBTQ community and how it has impacted me so far in my career. I’m grateful to have such amazing family, friends and fans that support me. You are my true allies ❤️🧡💛💚💙💜 LOVE IS LOVE #nyxcosmeticspartner #nyxcosmetics

node.text:
MERRY CHRISTMAS EVERYONE!!🌲😻🎅🏽☃️❄️💙💙💙Omg I can’t believe they have a cartoon of me in cardis Pepsi commercial! This is literally like a vivid memory I have in my head of one Christmas night @iamcardib and I had. The whole scenery and both of us looking out the window wishing for some Gifts 😻 It’s funny too because cardi’s favorite soda is Pepsi and I remember her going to the store every morning to get Pepsi and chop cheese and some
Cookies & chips hehehe. Ahh the memories this.☃️❄️ Happy holidays to you all! ❤️🤶🏽🕎

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hennessy💋 on September 03, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, cake and indoor.

node.text:
I still can’t believe aunties baby turned 3 years old 🥺💖🤗 Of course i cried lol🥲 She makes me so happy 😍💖 She is sooo smart, sweet & funny! My sunshine! I loveeee you soo much! 🎀💖✨
Im always lowkey when I’m with my niece,  I love spending quality time her. I be hands on with my niece all the time usually my clothes, hair and makeup ends up getting messy with paint /slime or playing for hours by the end of the day I look a hot mess 😭🤣🥰💖💖 idc as long as we spend our real quality time together 💖but Yea I still can’t believe my princess is 3! May god bless my niece. I’ll Always be here for you to love and protect and be the best auntie for you 💖 @kulturekiari
